Fixes #1615 

This fixes a performance issue caused by ExplorationStepsList$MyTreeNode. The problem was that drawing the list calls ExplorationStepsList$MyTreeNode.toString() on every node, which iterates over all subnodes. I replaced the toString function with one that simply returns the serialNr.

